title: Final Audit Report on Northup for Congress is Available
html:
News Releases, Media Advisories

November 13, 2003

ATTENTION WIRE SERVICES, DAYBOOK EDITORS:
FINAL AUDIT REPORT ON
NORTHUP FOR CONGRESS
The Federal Election Commission has made available the final audit report on Northup for Congress (KY). This audit covers the period of January 1, 2001 through December 31, 2002.

Contact: FEC Press Office (202) 694-1220, 999 E Street, NW
